, holotype, male terminalia. 36. Dorsal. 37. Ventral. Scale bar = ca. 0.5 mm. Abbreviations: c, cerci; gc, gonocoxite; gs, gonostylus; p, paramere; t9, tergite nine; vml, ventromedian lobes of gonocoxite.
